content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Service Gateway Firmware Version 3.0.13 September 24, 2024—Service Gateway Firmware Version 3.0.13 includes enhancements, bug fixes, and security updates for Service Gateway. This update includes the following changes: This update adds a bug fix for increasing storage for Service Gateway appliances deployed with AWS. This update corrects the invalid K8S certificate time caused by wrong RTC time on the Service Gateway appliance. This update enhances the iptables to accommodate a large number of ports. © 2025 Trend Micro Incorporated. All rights reserved.Search Knowledge Base
